result.title: Need for Speed: Most Wanted (Gameplay)
result.description:
“Need for Speed: Most Wanted” (2005) has a unique narrative structure that is driven by the player’s progression rather than a traditional linear storyline. The game follows an unnamed street racer, the player character, as they arrive in the fictional city of Rockport with a goal to become the most wanted racer by taking down the 15 racers on the Blacklist.

Original title: Need For Speed
First air date: May. 10, 2007
Last air date: Sep. 13, 2007
Seasons: 1
Episodes: 3
